ts/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />消化差<br />\n<br />\n2 日去一次大"},{"pid":"1c285e89f914243cbece5b75f63b1bf942d58d9c","tid":310273,"uid":1671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一年起碼肚痾10幾次 痾啲屎又黑又水咁 1日痾8、9次 成日出唔到街 煩死</blockquote><br />\n屌 我都試過屙黑屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望到嗰下嚇親"},{"pid":"b98dfb3da25be53cf061b7a428a80af82a7c35ec","tid":310273,"uid":1671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食米線好易瀨嘢，會痾幾日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好羨慕d人大魚大肉都無事</span></blockquote><br />\n紅字同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次食完大餐都要自己受返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321b4e5004aaa5dc627002c4f77ff8ee2ddaad56","tid":310273,"uid":1671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話說有次食完大排檔，腸胃炎入左廠<br />\n個姑娘話要驗屎，俾左個杯仔俾我裝屎<br />\n我幾經辛苦先屙到少少屎水出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知個姑娘話太少，驗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰下真係想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁最後點？姑娘有冇教你痾屎大法？</blockquote><br />\n佢叫我再屙過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後靠自己終於咇到啲屎碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用勝利者既表情望住個姑娘再俾杯屎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761f658450a7b3aa575790b92bc2fd58f43adc4b","tid":310273,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"一冷一熱野食溝埋就好易屙<br />\n多油野又係<br />\n一食完KFC炸雞再飲可樂例必要搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla