":310273,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b5ca81d752b8c57c253f313ddcd60e2601784ab","tid":310273,"uid":40228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一日痾三次屎，每次食完野就有屎痾<br />\n每次都正常屎，唔係肚痾<br />\n個人好瘦，唔知係咪因為唔吸收，油浸都唔肥<br />\n有冇人係咁，好想肥d呀</blockquote><br />\n一日三次屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好羨慕<br />\n我都吸收差，冇營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痾到人都癲，眼都鬆晒<br />\n好想肥呀</blockquote><br />\n但屙正常屎好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都增唔到肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一食得多就即刻肚屙屙返哂出黎<br />\n吸收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係, 得50KG<br />\n食完就屙,一肚痛就屙<br />\n吸收唔到好難有肉"},{"pid":"0b8291834735e5900184df125993fa39f820edd0","tid":310273,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"五寶散係最好既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長期陪伴左右"},{"pid":"70681feeb073ba200249f1d8e5323feb68223163","tid":310273,"uid":66565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"我都係，腸易激<br />\n正露丸跟身，去街多數去商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少飲凍野會好d"},{"pid":"2b2c87cf03922a477123a6060b8e196657637003","tid":310273,"uid":92179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"試下睇中醫調理下"},{"pid":"c5adfa913cf05ea671ea997deb4b4ba41bf392b5","tid":310273,"uid":1671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"