\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到幾位巴打pm我咩品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c101dd0411bc70622d6519e3ccc8c3fec7fa13f8","tid":310273,"uid":105324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"巴打們係咪腸易激?<br />\n我之前日日出門口前都痾4,5次<br />\n食完野就即刻急屎 食油膩啲嘅野或者辣野都好易肚痾<br />\n最後睇中醫食左一排中藥好返啲<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴打睇完西醫 驗過屎知自己唔係其他病 而係ibs 可以試下針灸或者中藥<br />\n另外緊張壓力大都有可能影響病情 所以盡可能做下運動放鬆個人<br />\n有啲人就食某類野先會肚痾 所以得閒就記低食咩會肚痾 避免食個啲野<br />\n如果有講錯野請見諒 最好都係問返醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef115da71e2b16f76d916a9ec0ad33dd5f99d9a","tid":310273,"uid":120719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"做愛太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badaa3f384007550f2715cb4351399e88379db7c","tid":310273,"uid":98413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"最慘次次去旅行超過5日就腸胃炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884a02d76622848dc7ab0d2f225a24d5d73e8a52","tid":310273,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最慘次次去旅行超過5日就腸胃炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一撚樣<br />\n去日本肚痛幾次<br />\n要即刻落車搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢去歐州<br />\n驚去到窮"},{"pid":"76d735c5b80743b2911c86394592e262590bede2","tid":310273,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最慘次次去旅行超過5日就腸胃炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一撚樣<br />\n去日本肚痛幾次<br />\n要即刻落車搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢去歐州<br />\n驚去到窮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：去台灣水土不服<img src